Package: phylobates
Type: Package
Title: Tidy utilities to tread in phylogenetic trees
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Théo Pannetier
Maintainer: Théo Pannetier <t.s.c.pannetier@rug.nl>
Description: A set of tools to work with phylogenetic trees, 
    including tidy revamps of ape and TreePar built upon tidyverse functions, 
    made compatible to work with ggplot.
